    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (such a gentle voice!)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (it seemed to float through space)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (softening the crude steel around us)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: Not at all,
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: I'm happy to have some company!
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: So where do you want to go?
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: '!!!'
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: Really? You haven't...
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: Decided where you're going to go next?
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (As I listened, I began to notice some things)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (her hologram carried no input lag)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (usually people in low-earth orbit)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (can easily travel to earth, but...)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (why would she want me to take her eyes)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (when she can just go herself?)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: ... Uhh.. What station are you in?
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: '!!'
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: '!!!!!'
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: ...Don't ask......Please.....
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 0
    speakerName: 
    text: ......
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (huh?)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: (ok, I'll leave the topic)
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: OK then! Well, have you though of somewhere
    waitAfterLine: 0
  - isPlayer: 1
    speakerName: 
    text: To spend a few precious hours in?
    waitAfterLine: 0
